description:
Danny welcomes Queen LeeAnne Locken from Bravo's Real Housewives of Dallas to the show. They spend an hour recapping the iconic second season of #RHOD, her role in Miss Congeniality, her compelling upbringing, Mariah Carey, and SO MUCH MORE. If you're a Housewives fan, you CANNOT miss this.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
